    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sheets, typically of paper or vellum, that were formerly parts of manuscripts or other volumes, but have been disconnected, separated, unattached, or otherwise removed from the volume.</Note_Text>
